channel.description: Hello everyone, I'm Sanket Makhija, Born Product Builder, Maker and Full Stack Developer. Coding from the last ~11 years. Currently re-imagining hacker news. NodeJS, TypeScript, ReactJS, NextJs, ChakraUI, AWS, Mysql, Redis, Netlify, Vercel. Happy to connect with all. DM is open.
